                <note rend="inline" type="source">714.44A15/133: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Guatemala</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Des Portes</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1940-02-27T19:00:00-05:00"
                            >February 27, 1940—7 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>11. Your no. 22, February 26, 11 a.m. You may inform President Ubico that his
                    suggestion with regard to the Belize negotiations will be transmitted to Mr.
                    Welles.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
